<%- include("includes/header") %>
<main class="flex p-32 gap-32">
  <%- include("includes/flash") %>
  <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
    <h1 class="text-6xl font-thin">Remember Writing?</h1>
    <p class="text-gray-400">
      Lorem ipsum dolor, sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Suscipit nostrum
      commodi dolor accusamus autem. Sunt similique maiores nihil eaque repellat
      voluptatem itaque eveniet odio sapiente tempore in deserunt, temporibus
      delectus reprehenderit labore earum aspernatur cupiditate incidunt
      veritatis ut. Commodi assumenda blanditiis saepe maiores corrupti at ea
      sunt, ipsum fugit voluptatibus.
    </p>
  </div>
  <form class="flex flex-col gap-4" action="/signup" method="post">
    <input
      type="text"
      name="username"
      class="border rounded px-2 w-72"
      placeholder="Username"
      required
    />
    <input
      type="password"
      name="password"
      class="border rounded px-2"
      placeholder="Password"
      required
    />
    <input
      type="email"
      name="email"
      class="border rounded px-2"
      placeholder="Email"
      required
    />
    <button
      type="submit"
      class="text-white block bg-green-600 rounded px-2 py-2"
    >
      Signup
    </button>
  </form>
</main>

